### Search flights
GET http://localhost:8081/api/flights/search?origin=DEL&destination=BOM&departureDate={{departureDate}}&passengers=1

### Search mock GDS/Skyscanner provider flights
GET http://localhost:8081/api/flights/provider-search?origin=DEL&destination=BOM&departureDate={{departureDate}}&passengers=1

### Get one flight
GET http://localhost:8081/api/flights/{{flightId}}

### Get one flight by flight number
GET http://localhost:8081/api/flights/numbers/SK101

### Check availability
GET http://localhost:8081/api/flights/{{flightId}}/availability?passengers=2

### Check availability by flight number
GET http://localhost:8081/api/flights/numbers/SK101/availability?passengers=2

### Create a seat hold
POST http://localhost:8081/api/flights/{{flightId}}/seat-holds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengerCount": 2
}

### Release a seat hold
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/flights/seat-holds/{{seatHoldId}}
